<p>Go to <strong>System » CMS » Newsletter » plentymarkets » Email filter</strong> to filter customer data and copy this data into specific email folders. For example, you can search for all customers who purchased a certain item during a specific time period. You can then use the folders when sending newsletters to these customer groups in the <a href="/en/crm/sending-newsletters#1000">CMS » Newsletter</a> menu.</p>
