<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="2000">2.3. Manually transmitting customer data</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the <strong>Carry out data transfer</strong> option to only transfer customer data for a specific customer type. This allows you to sort the plentymarkets customer types into different CleverReach groups.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Should I use the automatic transfer?</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you use the option <strong>Carry out data transfer</strong> in order to transfer customer data filtered by customer type, then you may have to deactivate the automatic transfer. The automatic transfer will transfer all new customer data without considering the different customer types.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
