</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Manually transmitting customer data:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » CMS » Newsletter » CleverReach</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter your <strong>API key</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the <strong>List ID</strong> of the group that you created in CleverReach.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Generate group attributes</strong>.<br>
→ Data fields will be set up in CleverReach. This way the data that you transfer can be saved and processed.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the CleverReach back end and open the group whose list ID you entered into plentymarkets.</p>
</li>
